        <img
            data-sizes="(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px"
            data-srcset="https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?quality=80 625w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=150,96&amp;quality=80 150w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=550,352&amp;quality=80 550w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=400,256&amp;quality=80 400w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=401,257&amp;quality=80 401w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=275,176&amp;quality=80 275w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=325,208&amp;quality=80 325w, https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?resize=600,384&amp;quality=80 600w"
            data-src="https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?w=625&#038;h=400&#038;quality=80"
            sizes="(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px"
            src=""
            alt="INDRANIL MUKHERJEE/AFP/Getty Images"
            style="width:auto;"
            class="image -fit -lazy"
        >
        <noscript>
            <img
                src="https://foreignpolicy.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/huawei16.jpg?w=625&#038;h=400&#038;quality=80"
                alt="INDRANIL MUKHERJEE/AFP/Getty Images"
                class="image -fit-3-2">
        </noscript>
        </a>
        </figure>
    <div class="list-text">
    <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2012/10/12/my-way-or-the-huawei/">
    <h3 class="hed">My Way Or the Huawei</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">The U.S. government&#039;s recent accusations against two Chinese companies are seriously overblown. 
</p>
</div>
<div class="meta-data -excerpt">
        <a
        href="https://foreignpolicy.com/category/analysis/argument/"
        class="department-name -excerpt">
        Argument    </a>
